She looked at Scorponok, "Commander, I'll be right back."

She turned and walked very quickly over to Quickstrike, "What happened? I 
heard a shot?"
She looked and saw Stingra.  Her arm was damaged and her hand was missing.  
She ran over to Stingra.
"Your injured.  I can help you with that if you like.  I can have it fixed 
up in no time at all if you'll let me."
